nodes.text: Rina Major was a planet located in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories that was the homeworld of the Blarina species, whose name meant "children of Rin". Blarina from Rina Major included Ohn Gos and Naka Iit, the latter of whom once finished fifth in soliloquy competition on his homeworld.
In Star Wars: Alien Archive, Rina Major is misidentified as Cona.
